<section id="about">
    <div class="about-container">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="profile-section">
                <img src="/portfolio/your-profile-image.jpg" alt="Profile Picture" />
                <a href="https://github.com/jessenhs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="github-link">
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                    GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="text-section">
                <p>I'm Jesse, a software developer with a growing passion for creating digital solutions. My journey into the world of programming has equipped me with a versatile skill set that allows me to work across different layers of application development.</p>
                <p>I approach each project with enthusiasm and a problem-solving mindset. My ability to adapt to different programming environments enables me to tackle diverse challenges and continuously expand my technical knowledge. I'm always eager to learn new technologies and improve my craft to deliver the best possible solutions.</p>
                <div class="skills">
                    <h3>Skills</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Web Development</li>
                        <li>Python</li>
                        <li>PHP</li>
                        <li>SQL</li>
                        <li>CSS</li>
                        <li>HTML</li>
                        <li>XAMPP</li>
                        <li>Astro Framework</li>
                        <li>Unity</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    #about {
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        background-color: #111;
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .about-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fff, #ccc);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        position: relative;
    }

    h2::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 60px;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fff, #666);
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .about-content {
        display: flex;
        gap: 4rem;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .profile-section {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .profile-section img {
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .profile-section img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.02);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .text-section {
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 300px;
    }

    p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #e0e0e0;
    }

    .skills {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .skills ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .skills li {
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #333, #444);
        padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .skills li:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #444, #555);
    }

    .github-link {
        color: #ccc;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #333, #444);
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .github-link:hover {
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #444, #555);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .about-container {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .profile-section img {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>